IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. GOVERNANCE-DEMO.
AUTHOR. CENTRA-NF.

ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
OS "Linux".
ARCH "x86_64".

DATA DIVISION.
VIDEO-MP4 data "sample.mp4".

GOVERNANCE DIVISION.
POLICY COMPLIANCE-POLICY FORMULA "G F (compress -> verify)".
REGULATION GDPR CLAUSE "Article 5 - Data minimization".
ACCESS-CONTROL USER "default" RESOURCE "data" ACTION "COMPRESS".
ACCESS-CONTROL USER "default" RESOURCE "data" ACTION "VERIFY-INTEGRITY".
AUDIT-LEDGER "Governance demo started".

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
COMPRESS data.
VERIFY-INTEGRITY data.
AUDIT-LEDGER "Operations completed successfully".